						<summary>

						<p>Rock in a field called ‘Sēshappa-maḍi’.</p>						

						<p>1584 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record refers to Bhīkshāvṛitti-ayya and seems to register a gift the details of which cannot be made out.</p>						

						<p>It is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Tāraṇa, Māgha ba. 14, Friday.</hi> On palaeographical grounds the record may be assigned to the 16th century in which case the details regularly correspond to <hi rend="bold">1584 A.D., January 31</hi> which might be the intended date.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
